代","createdAt":"2025-04-25T17:23:13"},{"id":"01967af6-be5e-707e-afe2-4a6a463565a7","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":4084,"content":"中肯","createdAt":"2025-04-28T13:55:13"},{"id":"01967bc8-8feb-70c4-86a9-6e2c9b4dcfbd","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22668,"content":"众阳三年没涨工资了，不信你随机拦个员工问问","createdAt":"2025-04-28T17:44:23"},{"id":"01969f9c-aafc-701f-927d-4e3c187f125f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":23172,"content":"千万！绝对！避雷众阳，谢谢。","createdAt":"2025-05-05T16:42:46"},{"id":"0196a8b3-7c3e-734e-9ba9-35fd81846496","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":23660,"content":"1","createdAt":"2025-05-07T11:04:17"},{"id":"0196afad-226b-70fc-b0d5-6e42f9dd5897","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":23228,"content":"老东家金现代，别的不说，至少按时发工资，工资从来没拖欠过，报销的话稍微慢点，但是也没有很慢，还是看领导审核，到了财务就快了，听说现在走高端不走外包了，还是很牛掰的","createdAt":"2025-05-08T19:34:41"},{"id":"01971c81-f167-7356-9a42-82f93a591f20","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":24615,"content":"这俩货半斤八两，众阳口碑倒数第二，金现代也没好哪去","createdAt":"2025-05-29T22:46:07"},{"id":"01973f31-f855-7332-9bff-b9f5b7956fab","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3346,"content":"在金现代待了6年了，感觉还行，哈哈哈，可能和部门有关系，听其他部门经常吐槽，但是自己部门还好吧","createdAt":"2025-06-05T16:25:28"},{"id":"0197acc3-a310-7197-a659-509f0b2558b0","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":25416,"content":"裁员厉害吗","createdAt":"2025-06-26T23:03:11"},{"id":"019c17ec-3eed-728e-9f6d-52a13e3cd032","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":25732,"content":"还是外包，加班出差严重","createdAt":"2026-02-01T14:38:04"},{"id":"019c17ef-fc12-7118-814f-cbb17da0fb1c","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":25732,"content":"金现代工资低，加班严重，离职率高，缺人的很，应该不怎么裁。","createdAt":"2026-02-01T14:42:09"},{"id":"019c17f0-9ceb-7394-94f6-427e6cb409d9","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":25732,"content":"倒一是谁哈哈","createdAt":"2026-02-01T14:42:50"}]